column5: for crying out loud....would they just stop and let me catch up for a moment!  I was looking into all this HD, DSI, Structure scan business....considering my options. Decided not to be limited to Lowrance....and to be quite honest a little dissappointed the way Lowrance seem to be going on a lot of their stuff, went to check out hummingbirds...to be greeted by something called 360 degree veiwing.....THATS IT....I AINT BUYING ANYTHING TILL NEXT YEAR WHEN I WILL BE ABLE TO GET A VIRTUAL HOLOGRAM READING ANYWHERE IN THE BOAT OR THE INSIDE LENS OF MY POLARIZED SHADES
Good Morning HAL  The fish will be biting on 1/16th oz chartreuse tipped today
That was a good film....but i liked Darkstar better.   <iframe width="560" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/luaRtGn2tsI" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
